  "title": "Supply Chain Assistant (Procurement) - Up to $3000",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p><p>· Responsible for full spectrum of purchasing process (sourcing, quotation enquiry, price negotiation, placement of orders and delivery arrangement).</p><p>· Data Entry of Purchase Orders (PO).</p><p>· Maintain accurate records of procurement activities, including contracts, purchase orders, and supplier performance.</p><p>· Ensure proper documentation and filing as per ISO guidelines.</p><p>· Develop and maintain relationships with suppliers, negotiate prices and terms of contracts, and monitor supplier performance.</p><p>· Sourcing suppliers and purchase electrical equipment, spare parts, and other electronic components.</p><p>· Ensure timely delivery of materials and services.</p><p>· Manage inventory levels to ensure adequate supply without excessive stockpiling and conduct stock take.</p><p>· Identify and implement opportunities for cost savings and process improvement in the procurement function.</p><p>· Collaborate with cross-functional teams to ensure alignment between procurement activities and overall project goals.</p><p>· Any ad-hoc duties assigned by the supervisor.</p><p><strong>Job requirements:</strong></p><p>· Minimum Diploma in Business Administration, Supply Chain Management, or a related field.</p><p>· At least 2 years of relevant experience.</p><p>· Strong understanding of procurement processes and practices, including sourcing, negotiation, and contract management.</p><p>· Possess electrical knowledge, experience in dealing with freight forwarders and coming from marine & offshore industry will be an added advantage.</p><p>· Excellent communication and negotiation skills, with the ability to build and maintain effective relationships with suppliers and internal stakeholders.</p><p>· Willing to do paperwork.<br /><br /><br /><strong>Interested and suitable candidate kindly click quick apply. Resume will be forwarded to Stepfan Soon Yit</strong></p><p><strong>We regret that only suitable candidate will be notified.</strong></p><p><strong>GEMS Recruit/EA License : 23C1459</strong></p><p><strong>EA Personnel No : R24120893 (Stepfan Soon Yit)</strong></p>",
